{"tid":1184500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[做7-11的巴絲] 或鍾意儲7仔印花換野的巴絲請進","createTime":"2019-06-03T15:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T07:16:41.000Z","uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f50838ee5344d18eeca7de4ff9225fef38c172a0","tid":1184500,"uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"話説 我喺7仔儲左好撚多個印花<br />\n點知啲換領品無哂要訂貨 要由2月訂到5月尾<br />\n但3個月後 我果然係唔記得左個攞貨日期過撚左期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先我至醒起 再摷返張單出黎<br />\n<br />\n請問有無巴絲有過以上經驗 <br />\n可唔可以講下最後拎唔拎得返啲換領品<br />\n啲印花儲得好撚辛苦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲有無機會攞返我啲Sanrio碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認係我自己無腦唔記得個換領期限<br />\n屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日放工會即刻去果間7仔問下"},{"pid":"b606ee763898f5287932a9be529c9fe1e1224a5b","tid":1184500,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"應該冇，之前試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3fd4aa2e1a0a71f1c5e37b6ddcd6c68fb97ce0","tid":1184500,"uid":37136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:16:29.000Z","msg":"鋪有貨 你有單<br />\n實比你拎架<br />\n最驚冇人拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaddd49437891d839e6cb957c72b4b4aa3d1a4c","tid":1184500,"uid":216170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"正常會俾你 如果唔係遲得太多"}]}